> 2.2.13, I just saw it a few minutes ago. Immediately after, I had
> occaision to shutdown again, and it worked without trouble. I have no clue
> as to what is causing this. I heard whisperings of APM problems from
> someone, but I don't have APM enabled in the kernel.
> 
